==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ambrotype
<hw>Am"bro*type</hw> <pr>(-t⟦imac⟧p)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>'a`mbrotos</grk> immortal + <ets>-type</ets>.]</ety>
<fld>(Photog.)</fld> <def>A picture taken on a plate of prepared glass,
in which the lights are represented in silver, and the shades are
produced by a dark background visible through the unsilvered portions of
the glass.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ambry</ent>⟦br⟧
